  <brief_title>Studying Blood Samples in Young Patients With Cytopenia After a Donor Stem Cell Transplant</brief_title>
  <official_title>Serial Analysis of Chimerism in Patients With Refractory Cytopenia (RC) Transplanted With Reduced Intensity Conditioning (RIC)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>European Working Group of MDS in Childhood</agency>
