  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        DISEASE CHARACTERISTICS:

          -  Diagnosed with refractory cytopenia

               -  Hypocellular bone marrow and normal karyotype

          -  Underwent stem cell transplantation (SCT) from an HLA identical (8/8) sibling, an HLA
             identical (10/10) relative, or an HLA identical or single allelic disparate unrelated
             donor

               -  Received a preparative regimen including either thiotepa or fludarabine phosphate

          -  Concurrently enrolled on EWOG-MDS-2006

        PATIENT CHARACTERISTICS:

          -  Not specified

        PRIOR CONCURRENT THERAPY:

          -  See Disease Characteristics
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
